install elm runtime
    https://44a95588fe4cc47efd96-ec3c2a753a12d2be9f23ba16873acc23.ssl.cf2.rackcdn.com/Elm-Platform-0.18.exe

install NPM
    https://www.npmjs.com/get-npm

install elm format
    open powershell
    type: npm install -g elm-format@0.6.1-alpha
    close powershell

install Visual Studio Code
    https://code.visualstudio.com/download

install Elm extension for vscode
    open Extensions (View -> Extensions)
    search for "elm"
    select elm Language support for visual studio code
    press green install button

install missing packages \ build project
    open Integrated terminal (View -> Integrated Terminal)
    type: elm-make src\Main.elm
    (if asked to confirm, type: y)

Note, the full versions of elm-make is (make sure to change output directory to your repo location):
    elm-make Src\Main.elm --output=C:\Projects\NavCare\HC360-Integration-UserInterfaceEnhancements-Matt2-joe\trunk\Care-24-7\Care-24-7-MVC\Scripts\app.js